                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que ton cœur prenne ma défense.\nPassant, de mon dernier séjour !\nJe mourus sans rendre une offense :\nMon sort fut une longue enfance,\nEt ma pensée un long amour !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Sur moi lentement éveillée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Femme, je n’ai pas fui mon sort ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et sous mes larmes effeuillée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Dans mes doux sentiments raillée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Je pleurais, et j’aimais encor !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sur moi lentement éveillée,\nFemme, je n’ai pas fui mon sort ;\nEt sous mes larmes effeuillée,\nDans mes doux sentiments raillée,\nJe pleurais, et j’aimais encor !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Auprès de cette cendre éteinte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Demeure un instant par pitié !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Sous l’urne tiède et sans empreinte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Que je rêve un moment la plainte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "De l’amour ou de l’amitié.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Auprès de cette cendre éteinte\nDemeure un instant par pitié !\nSous l’urne tiède et sans empreinte,\nQue je rêve un moment la plainte\nDe l’amour ou de l’amitié."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Car on dit que longtemps encore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "L’âme retourne au monument,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Glissant du ciel à chaque aurore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Pour épier ce qu’elle adore…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et que parfois c’est vainement !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car on dit que longtemps encore\nL’âme retourne au monument,\nGlissant du ciel à chaque aurore,\nPour épier ce qu’elle adore…\nEt que parfois c’est vainement !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Si l’attente, effroi de ma vie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Doit aussi tourmenter ma mort,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Si pas un cœur ne m’a suivie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Parle-moi, toi ! je t’en supplie :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Dis mon nom et pleure mon sort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si l’attente, effroi de ma vie,\nDoit aussi tourmenter ma mort,\nSi pas un cœur ne m’a suivie,\nParle-moi, toi ! je t’en supplie :\nDis mon nom et pleure mon sort."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Bon passant ! si ta voix est tendre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Jamais je n’oublierai ta voix.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Parle-moi ! guéris-moi d’attendre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Dis mon nom : je croirai l’entendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Comme on me l’a dit une fois !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bon passant ! si ta voix est tendre,\nJamais je n’oublierai ta voix.\nParle-moi ! guéris-moi d’attendre ;\nDis mon nom : je croirai l’entendre\nComme on me l’a dit une fois !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Si tu vois une fleur sauvage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Croître et trembler sur mon tombeau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Cueille à la mort son pâle hommage ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Emporte cette frêle image",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "D’un être plus aimant que beau.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si tu vois une fleur sauvage\nCroître et trembler sur mon tombeau,\nCueille à la mort son pâle hommage ;\nEmporte cette frêle image\nD’un être plus aimant que beau."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Prends-moi, sous ce fragile emblème,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Comme un talisman pour tes jours ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "S’il recèle un peu de moi-même,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Cache-le sur un cœur qui t’aime ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Et ce cœur t’aimera toujours !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Prends-moi, sous ce fragile emblème,\nComme un talisman pour tes jours ;\nS’il recèle un peu de moi-même,\nCache-le sur un cœur qui t’aime ;\nEt ce cœur t’aimera toujours !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Jamais une main qui sépare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "N’osera s’étendre entre vous ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "L’amour ne sera plus avare ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Et si tout l’enfer ne t’égare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Toi ! tu ne seras point jaloux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jamais une main qui sépare\nN’osera s’étendre entre vous ;\nL’amour ne sera plus avare ;\nEt si tout l’enfer ne t’égare,\nToi ! tu ne seras point jaloux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "J’ai porté bonheur sur la terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "À ceux qui pleuraient devant moi :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Une larme est un saint mystère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Va ! de ta pitié solitaire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Cette fleur m’acquitte envers toi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’ai porté bonheur sur la terre\nÀ ceux qui pleuraient devant moi :\nUne larme est un saint mystère.\nVa ! de ta pitié solitaire\nCette fleur m’acquitte envers toi !"
        }
    ],
